text:
Estelle Millot (born 21 December 1993) is a French water polo player. She participated at the 2011 Summer Universiade, 2013 Summer Universiade, 2015 World Water Polo Championship, 2015 Summer Universiade, and 2017 World Water Polo Championship.
She plays in the French pro A championship and in the National team.
She is a trainer at Olympique Nice Natation.
